## Interface: 11508
## Title: TOGBankClassic
## Notes: A simple way to aggregate, view and request items from the inventories of multiple guild bank alts.
## Author: Dominion-Myzrael, GrumpyPlayers (also known as <SG>Soul), Lothsahn, Huntmehuntme-Myzrael, Pimptasty
## Version: @project-version@

## SavedVariables: TOGBankClassicDB, TOGBankClassicIconDB, TOGBankClassicOptionDB, TOGBankClassicDB_DebugLog, TOGBankClassic_PerfMetrics, TOGBankClassic_PerfEnabled, TOGBankClassic_DebugLogEnabled
## Dependencies: Ace3, VersionCheck-1.0
## OptionalDeps: Bagnon
## X-Curse-Project-ID: 1400244

# Libraries (use external Ace3 - only load non-Ace3 libraries).
# LibStub is bundled with Ace3 (which loads first via ## Dependencies), so we
# don't ship a redundant copy. LibStub's built-in versioning handles any future
# double-load gracefully if a vendored copy ever returns.
Libs/LibDataBroker-1.1/LibDataBroker-1.1.lua
Libs/LibDBIcon-1.0/LibDBIcon-1.0.lua
Libs/AceCommQueue-1.0/AceCommQueue-1.0.lua

# Modules
Modules/Constants.lua
Modules/Output.lua
Modules/Performance.lua
# Static data tables (generated by tools/build-itemdb.py from wago.tools DB2
# dumps; load early so anything that queries item class has them available)
Modules/Static/ItemDB.lua
Modules/Static/SuffixDB.lua
Modules/DeltaComms.lua
Modules/Bank.lua
Modules/Chat.lua
Modules/Database.lua
Modules/Events.lua
Modules/Guild.lua
